data.description: Discover the hidden gem of St. Francis! This townhome floorplan has everything you could want and more! Like entertaining? Head straight to the open-concept kitchen and check out the HUGE center island with breakfast bar and soaring, valued ceilings - the perfect setting for dinner parties or early morning breakfast. Don't miss the stainless appliances. Whether you're hosting a gathering or would rather enjoy a quiet evening under the stars, you can head outside to the private deck or head to the walkout basement and relax on the patio. When you're ready to get some work done, ascend to the loft, a versatile space ideal for productivity. At the end of the day, unwind in your primary bedroom and pick out your outfit for tomorrow in your walk-in closet. Schedule a viewing today and discover the perfect place to create lasting memories! Minutes to shopping, restaurants, and nearby schools/parks.
